title: The Philadelphia 76ers Exit Interview | Weekends With Wos
description:
Wos is joined by Derek Bodner from The Athletic to discuss the comments made by Joel Embiid, James Harden, and Doc Rivers after the 76ers were eliminated from the NBA playoffs. They detail each of their histories with the team, speculate on their futures, and talk about the possible offseason moves Daryl Morey can make for Philadelphia going forward.
Host: Wosny Lambre
Guest: Derek Bodner
Producer: Chris Sutton
